issues.description: Profile "Profile_enc52_bay8" Ethernet connection 1 does not have an associated network. This connection will not be migrated because OneView does not allow server profile connections without an assigned network.
issues.recommendation: To migrate the server profile connection, assign a network to this connection. If virtual MAC addresses are configured, assigning a network to this connection will preserve these addresses.
